23#include "mpfr-impl.h"
24
25/* Using memcpy is a few slower than swapping by hand. */
26
27void
28mpfr_swap (mpfr_ptr u, mpfr_ptr v)
29{
30 mpfr_prec_t p1, p2;
31 mpfr_sign_t s1, s2;
32 mpfr_exp_t e1, e2;
33 mp_limb_t *m1, *m2;
34
35 p1 = MPFR_PREC(u);
36 p2 = MPFR_PREC(v);
37 MPFR_PREC(v) = p1;
38 MPFR_PREC(u) = p2;
39
40 s1 = MPFR_SIGN(u);
41 s2 = MPFR_SIGN(v);
42 MPFR_SIGN(v) = s1;
43 MPFR_SIGN(u) = s2;
44
45 e1 = MPFR_EXP(u);
46 e2 = MPFR_EXP(v);
47 MPFR_EXP(v) = e1;
48 MPFR_EXP(u) = e2;
49
50 m1 = MPFR_MANT(u);
51 m2 = MPFR_MANT(v);
52 MPFR_MANT(v) = m1;
53 MPFR_MANT(u) = m2;
54}
